item.description:
@FastBallz wrote:

[quote=“shadow235, post:5, topic:97187”][quote author=FastBawlz link=topic=139896.msg1344669#msg1344669 date=1179633606]

[quote author=shadow235 link=topic=139896.msg1344629#msg1344629 date=1179633213]

Sorry… But what is Board… Learn to spell?..

Anyways… 3rd one looks ripped

And the rest suck…
[/quote]Yea, I’m not a graphics master. Postive encouragement is better then telling everyone they suck. Get a life.

I would say something nice… But there isn’t anything nice to say…

[ul][] The duck on the first one is to streched
[] The text sucks and it doesn’t go with the bluish ocean like thing
[] Halo 3 part of the text is really nice, But the shadow part sucks… (Which makes me think you ripped it
[] 4th one is text with a face… Congratulations?[/ul]

[/quote]You can say try better instead of dissing every single one.[/quote]

See I do say that to alot of people that try?.. People that read tuts and things…? You know the things people with “No Lifes” Like you mentioned do…

See but a Face + Text + Black background , Thats not trying…
